{"tid":48163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【柏林恐襲】IS承認發動襲擊 上月曾發「孤狼式貨車襲擊」指引","createTime":"2016-12-21T01:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T01:23:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea236b249a234f49e6e18ef4370f9fd13333a21","tid":48163,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:23:44.000Z","msg":"德國柏林周一貨車撞聖誕市集，極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）承認是他們所為。<br />\n<br />\nIS在其「喉舌」阿馬克（Amaq）新聞社表示，施襲者是「IS士兵」，響應號召，針對「十字軍聯盟」的市民。<br />\n<br />\n今年7月法國尼斯貨車撞人群，IS亦承認責任。上月，IS在網上雜誌《Rumiyah》發出指引，教獨行施襲者如何用貨車施襲。文中指出，貨車是「對付異教徒的最安全簡單武器之一」，建議選用有相當速度的重型貨車，又指出市集、節慶活動、巡遊、政治集會是理想目標。<br />\n<br />\n文章教施襲者用字條寫明所隸屬的伊斯蘭組織，如「我是IS士兵」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／德新社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56072921&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56072921%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161221&d=2CcPM0vuG8RefkPM5DztOmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f46944ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56072921%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161221&h=cec95a0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56072921&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161221</a>"}]}